{"tid":2017101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢女子2月在陽台敲鑼呼救，哀求政府救治病母，如今也加入了聲討《武漢日記》的行列","createTime":"2020-05-15T01:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T10:21:30.000Z","uid":48040,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"976efcd545c77fe24d44c639f7153d97e133c670","tid":2017101,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:42:06.000Z","msg":"所有逃過武漢肺炎一劫的人，都成為了更加堅定的小粉紅。<br />\n<br />\n2月份疫情最嚴重的時候，武漢有一位女子，因為自己母親雙肺全白、生命垂危也得不到醫治，於是在自家陽台敲鑼呼救。後來，在熱心網友的宣傳下，終於獲得政府「皇恩浩蕩」，「恩賜」一張床位給她母親。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vMu9DmC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMu9DmC.png&h=b28e32ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位女子後來乾脆將自己微博的名字改為「敲鑼的我」，粉絲數量可觀，成為了另類的網紅。<br />\n再後來，作家方方寫了一本《武漢日記》，紀錄疫情期間武漢人民的慘況，還翻譯成了英文在世界各地出版。此舉觸怒了小粉紅以及《環球時報》，中國人紛紛指責方方抹黑中國。而此書也提到了這位敲鑼呼救的女士。於是，網友紛紛向「敲鑼的我」詢問，到底她對方方的立場是怎麼樣的。<br />\n沈默了數天之後，「敲鑼的我」終於表態，自己堅決擁護小粉紅：<br />\n-「（方方）太噁心了。」<br />\n-「我就是個升斗小民，還要贍養父母，扶養子女，為生活奔波。請方方不要把我寫進你的作品裡，我不想出國。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1HvnOn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1HvnOn.jpg&h=afcce4b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以話，「國家昏亂有忠臣」，不過呢班「忠臣」其實都不過是奴隸。<br />\n<br />\n～～～～～～～～～～～～～～～～<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4nzUThz8BvI&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=f32665bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI</a><br />\n我們頻道出版的書：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KYMtqu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KYMtqu&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=5188ad43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KYMtqu</a>"},{"pid":"ac1eb29450a4224c1459d3a7665c3f210fa35d7c","tid":2017101,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UJdRRJP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUJdRRJP.jpg&h=d939f91d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12a58ac70318385951b68df91a83ba69e184c860","tid":2017101,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:52:35.000Z","msg":"幫手打tvb戰線 借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［cctvb我屌你老母］去無良廣告商fb洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2017022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2017022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5886356669031e5df6bb97065624106e6a69f691","tid":2017101,"uid":246118,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"芝麻人真係無一個是蘑菇的<br />\n<br />\n幫完你，仲要畀你話，死咗去算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c78ccfb612c99f073e4855af48446244c6e0a9","tid":2017101,"uid":118120,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:58:17.000Z","msg":"不嬲都話佢地o係短時間內會o係共產黨統治既受害者<br />\n時間一過又會變番共產黨既支持者<br />\n佢地發生咩事都唔洗你可憐<br />\n因為佢地由始至終都會話香港抗爭者係暴徒"},{"pid":"cfd4a1067d58c049554c50d4151909cd80ec3cbf","tid":2017101,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"咁佢老母有冇死？"},{"pid":"6e3462e31168ad2f7eab01056ab221184acf7afb","tid":2017101,"uid":48040,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cfd4a1067d58c049554c50d4151909cd80ec3cbf","tid":2017101,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"咁佢老母有冇死？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:05:50.000Z","msg":"就係冇，所以現在講風涼話。"},{"pid":"380e86d29d4a235e9258ae1b2bb059795430a2f3","tid":2017101,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鐵拳打唔到"},{"pid":"371df2d7fdb0cef959f68b22531839cb457f0ed9","tid":2017101,"uid":118120,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"6e3462e31168ad2f7eab01056ab221184acf7afb","tid":2017101,"uid":48040,"like":6,"dislike":0,"sco